data.description:
Come check out this beautiful home that has four bedrooms, two full bathrooms, wood-burning fireplace, on a corner lot. 
Nice backyard with a large screened-in porch with a privacy fence and no HOAs here. Close to Fort Liberty, shopping, restaurants, and entertainment. The seller is offering $3,000 in seller concessions to an acceptable offer.
